---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout page="about-me">
	<section
		class="flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-6 px-4 text-center md:px-8 lg:items-start lg:gap-8 lg:text-left"
	>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:items-start">
			<div class="flex max-w-96 lg:w-full">
				<img src="/john.jpg" class="aspect-square rounded-full object-cover lg:w-full" />
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:max-w-[64ch] lg:w-full">
				<h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-none text-jk-purple sm:text-3xl">
					ABOUT JOHN <span class="font-emoji">ðŸ˜Ž</span>
				</h1>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-jk-purple sm:text-xl">
					Product Designer | Product Manager
				</h2>
				<p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
					Welcome to my portfolio! I am an innovative product designer based in Lagos,
					renowned for <span class="font-semibold text-jk-purple"
						>delivering exceptional user-centered designs solutions and driving business
						growth</span
					> in the dynamic blockchain and Web3 industry.
				</p>
				<p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
					Additionally, I am also a product manager, enabling me to contribute not only to
					the design aspect but also to <span class="text-jk-purple">
						the strategic planning, development, launch, and management of products and
						services.
					</span>
				</p>
				<p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
					In Web3, I have extensive experience working in <span class="text-jk-purple"
						>consumer techs, asset management, DAOs, NFT marketplaces, DEXs, payments,
						B2B, and developer tools.</span
					> I am also open to working and providing more user-centric solutions in other sectors
					of blockchain and Web3.
				</p>
				<p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
					I'm comfortable wearing multiple hats and switching them between <span
						class="text-jk-purple">product desing and product management.</span
					>
				</p>

				<p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
					When I'm not working, I find purpose in community building in the blockchain and
					Web3 space.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section
		class="flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-6 px-4 text-center md:px-8 lg:items-start lg:gap-8 lg:text-left"
	>
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
			<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-jk-purple">What I can do</h2>
				<a
					class="flex h-9 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-jk-purple px-6 text-sm text-jk-white duration-200 hover:bg-jk-purple/80"
					>VIEW MY CV</a
				>
			</div>
			<p class="text-start text-sm">If you can name it, I can do it.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
